											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Mystra gestures, and the comet on Gale's chest begins to glow, the magic of Karsus being drawn from his chest at last. He nods his thanks at mystra, who smiles and disappers. Then, Gale closes his eyes, contentment on his face, and lets her spell do its work. As the magic is drawn forth, Gale's symbol in the sky begins to fade/flicker. Then - with a brilliant FLASH it is gone. The outer planes are at peace once again, as is Gale." />
